<subSubSection id="413EB6711D46426410D289763E718F48" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" type="remark">
<paragraph id="D020A53265FD80FBF075996A43FD76BE" pageId="6" pageNumber="41">Remark.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5C9FD24B0A5989CF1438F91B71F4FD5D" pageId="6" pageNumber="41">
<bibRefCitation id="2A51096482B16F3B41489272CAC4A4D5" author="Pang, XF" journalOrPublisher="Science Press, China, Beijing" pageId="12" pageNumber="47" title="Coleoptera: Coccinellidae II. Economic Entomology China" year="1979">Pang and Mao (1979)</bibRefCitation>
transferred 
<taxonomicName id="4CE1FE4114FA0506BAD8002738DF6CEA" authority="Dieke, 1947" authorityName="Dieke" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afissa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afissa siamensis" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="siamensis">Afissa siamensis</taxonomicName>
Dieke into 
<taxonomicName id="9BEE6A9FF9259530B4E24CD71334B88D" authority="Dieke, 1947" authorityName="Dieke" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidenta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidenta" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Afidenta</taxonomicName>
without any explanation. However, a detailed examination of 
<taxonomicName id="6D8E0277560A978BD01F9E90CFF13A08" authority="Dieke, 1947" authorityName="Dieke" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidenta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidenta siamensis" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="siamensis">Afidenta siamensis</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4A69F682A752E1BD718F610C361C3071" authority="Dieke, 1947" authorityName="Dieke" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidenta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidenta misera" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="misera">Afidenta misera</taxonomicName>
left no doubt that they do not belong to a same genus, and that diagnostic characters of 
<taxonomicName id="FBD252C1210BD82A292340D9FB995B8A" authority="Dieke, 1947" authorityName="Dieke" authorityYear="1947" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidenta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidenta siamensis" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="siamensis">Afidenta siamensis</taxonomicName>
match 
<taxonomicName id="F4F506854D9C6175748E98ED5F939B44" authority="Kapur, 1955" authorityName="Kapur" authorityYear="1955" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidentula" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidentula" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Afidentula</taxonomicName>
. Thus this species in formally transfered to the genus 
<taxonomicName id="CE6ADC61844CEEBC4DC88DC66B99C6E1" authority="Kapur, 1955" authorityName="Kapur" authorityYear="1955" class="Insecta" family="Coccinellidae" genus="Afidentula" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Afidentula" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="41" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Afidentula</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
